OL,5, Jeremy Hunt has said the Conservatives 
OL,6, are committed to keeping the triple    
OL,7, lock system to decide rises in the     
OL,8, state pension if they win the election.
OL,10,FThe chancellor confirmed the policy    
OL,11,Fpledge, which means the increase in the
OL,12,Fstate pension is the highest of average
OL,13,Fearnings growth, inflation or 2.5%.    
OL,15,FHe told Sunday with Laura Kuenssberg he
OL,16,Fwas confident the "expensive" promise  
OL,17,Fwould be paid by growing the economy.  
OL,19,FLabour said it was "committed to       
OL,20,Fretaining" the triple lock.            
